sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para: The external interfaces of KDBit_MQB are described by the Component Diagram "Interfaces" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.ECU_DIAG_Chorus.KDBit_MQB.SW Architecture.Static

A part of the external interfaces used by KDBit_MQB is provided by the component "RTE Light QM" and includes generated interfaces: "sw.sys.chorus_main_doc\mc_sw\cdd\KDBit_MQB\KDBit_MQB\c\cfg\sst\KDBit_MQB_Sst.xlsx"
see also Component Diagram "SW Architecture" at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.KDBit_MQB.SW Architecture

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The module has dependencies to the following modules.
The external dependencies of KDBit_MQB are as described in the SWA present in EA: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.KDBit_MQB.SW Architecture
